    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this car\u2014it is in absolute mint condition! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still looks and feels like it just left the showroom. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept spotless and running perfectly. If you're looking for a ride that's basically brand new and ready for its next adventure, this is definitely the one for you. Shoot me a message if you want to take a look!",
