    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the high-revving S54B32 power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, showing zero rattle and optimal compression across all cylinders. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. Finished in a flawless coat with an interior free of bolster wear or dead pixels, this M3 retains its factory-correct mechanical tolerances and performance envelope.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
