    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its deep, luster-filled finish and pristine body lines without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Inside, the premium leather remains soft and unmarked, still carrying that distinctive new-car scent, while every dial and button operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history and an engine bay so clean it reflects the care of a dedicated enthusiast. This isn't just a pre-owned vehicle; it is a showroom-grade specimen that performs exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. Truly a turn-key opportunity for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
