      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, currently maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen exhibits a flawless exterior finish paired with an interior that remains in an untouched state, devoid of wear or compromise. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new machine. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a truly unblemished example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
