    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won\u2019t find another one this clean\u2014it\u2019s in total showroom condition and has been babied since day one! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. I've kept it garaged and serviced religiously, so it's ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
