    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a complete VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the signature telepathic steering feel. The exterior finish and interior upholstery are flawless, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical stewardship. No deferred maintenance; purely turn-key performance.",
